---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<style>
  .about-me-card {
    background-color: #161b22; /* Terminal dark background */
    border: 1px solid #58a6ff; /* Neon blue border */
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    color: #c9d1d9; /* Light text */
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    padding: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .about-me-title {
    color: #ff79c6; /* Pink Title */
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-me-text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .about-me-list {
    color: #8b949e; /* Soft gray */
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .about-me-list li {
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  .paragraph {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me" class="about-me-card">
  <div class="about-me-text">
    <p>
      Hello! My name is Jordan, and I'm currently a full-time Student, pursing my degree for computer science at Full Sail.
      <br />
      My skillset includes:
    </p>

    <ul class="about-me-list">
      <li>Java</li>
      <li>Lua</li>
      <li>C++</li>
      <li>Astro (Learning)</li>
      <li>GDScript (Learning)</li>
      <li>Unreal Visual Scripting (Learning)</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="paragraph">
      Beyond coding, I have a passion for design, 3D modeling, and cars. I also enjoy collecting old flagship phonesâ€”they represent a bygone era that fascinates me.
    </p>

    <p class="paragraph">
      I'm always eager to expand my skillset and find the right solution for every project I work on.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
